trans-unit.source: Extends design-time behavior for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> Web server control.
trans-unit.target: Estende o comportamento de tempo de design do controle de servidor Web <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" />.

trans-unit.source: Extend the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner> class if you want to create a designer for a class that extends the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> Web server control.
trans-unit.target: Estender o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner> classe se você quiser criar um designer para uma classe que estende o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> controle de servidor Web.

trans-unit.source: The following code example shows how to extend the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner> class and display debugging information on the design surface in case of an error.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir mostra como estender o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner> classe e exibir informações sobre o design de depuração de superfície no caso de erro.

trans-unit.source: The following code example shows how to associate a control class with the designer defined in the preceding example.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir mostra como associar uma classe de controle com o designer definido no exemplo anterior.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection" /> object for this designer.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection" /> para este designer.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection" /> associated with this designer.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection" /> associado a este designer.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection" /> to which regions associated with the wizard control are added.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection" /> à qual as regiões associadas ao controle de assistente são adicionadas.

trans-unit.source: Creates a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion" /> object for each step associated with the underlying wizard control, and then adds it to the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Cria um objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion" /> para cada etapa associada ao controle de assistente subjacente e, em seguida, adiciona-o ao objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection" /> object associated with this designer.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection" /> associado a esse designer.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection" /> associated with this designer.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection" /> associado a este designer.

trans-unit.source: Converts the child controls associated with the underlying wizard control to a custom navigation template.
trans-unit.target: Converte os controles filho associados ao controle de assistente subjacente em um modelo de navegação personalizada.

trans-unit.source: The exception that occurred.
trans-unit.target: A exceção que ocorreu.

trans-unit.source: Gets the HTML that provides information about the specified exception.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o HTML que fornece informações sobre a exceção especificada.

trans-unit.source: This method is typically called after an error has been encountered at design time.
trans-unit.target: Esse método normalmente é chamado depois que foi encontrado um erro em tempo de design.

trans-unit.source: The HTML for the specified exception.
trans-unit.target: O HTML para a exceção especificada.

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates how to override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.GetErrorDesignTimeHtml%2A> method to display debugging information on the design surface in case of an error.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir demonstra como substituir o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.GetErrorDesignTimeHtml%2A> método para exibir informações de depuração na superfície de design, no caso de erro.

trans-unit.source: The control element being designed.
trans-unit.target: O elemento de controle que está sendo criado.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the designer and loads the specified component.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa o designer e carrega o componente especificado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor" /> objects that represent the properties of the component's base class.
trans-unit.target: Os objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor" /> que representam as propriedades da classe base do componente.

trans-unit.source: The keys in the dictionary of properties are property names.
trans-unit.target: As chaves no dicionário de propriedades são nomes de propriedade.

trans-unit.source: Exposes the properties associated with each default step through the property grid on the designer tool.
trans-unit.target: Expõe as propriedades associadas a cada etapa padrão por meio da grade de propriedades na ferramenta de designer.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A> method provides a way to add items to the dictionary of properties that a designer exposes.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A> método fornece uma maneira de adicionar itens ao dicionário de propriedades que expõe um designer.

trans-unit.source: The keys in the dictionary of properties are the names of the properties.
trans-unit.target: As chaves no dicionário de propriedades são os nomes das propriedades.

trans-unit.source: The objects are of type <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>.
trans-unit.target: Os objetos são do tipo <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>.

trans-unit.source: You can directly modify the dictionary that is accessible through the <paramref name="properties" /> parameter, or you can leave it unchanged.
trans-unit.target: Você pode modificar diretamente o dicionário que pode ser acessado por meio de <paramref name="properties" /> parâmetro, ou você pode deixá-la inalterada.

trans-unit.source: If you are overriding the <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.PreFilterProperties(System.Collections.IDictionary)" /> method, call the base implementation before you perform your own filtering.
trans-unit.target: Se você está substituindo o <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.PreFilterProperties(System.Collections.IDictionary)" /> método, chame a implementação base antes de executar seu próprio processo de filtragem.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the designer uses the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> control itself to generate the design-time HTML or uses a temporarily created copy.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o designer usa o próprio controle <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> para gerar o HTML em tempo de design ou usa uma cópia criada temporariamente.

trans-unit.source: Always <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: Sempre <see langword="true" />.

trans-unit.source: When the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property is `true`, the designer uses a temporary copy of the wizard control to generate the design-time HTML; when the value of <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> is `false`, the designer uses the wizard control itself to generate the design-time HTML.
trans-unit.target: Quando o valor da <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> é de propriedade `true`, o designer usa uma cópia temporária do controle do Assistente para gerar o HTML de tempo de design; quando o valor de <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> é `false`, o designer usa o próprio controle do Assistente para gerar o HTML em tempo de design.

trans-unit.source: The value of <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> modifies the return value of the designer's <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O valor de <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> modifica o valor de retorno do designer de <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: When <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> is `true`, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> returns a copy of the wizard control.
trans-unit.target: Quando <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> é `true`, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> retorna uma cópia do controle wizard.

trans-unit.source: When <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> is `false`, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> returns the wizard control itself.
trans-unit.target: Quando <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> é `false`, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> retorna o próprio controle do assistente.

trans-unit.source: If the wizard control is marked with a class-level <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute> attribute, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute> is ignored, because the value of <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> is always `true`.
trans-unit.target: Se o controle do assistente está marcado com um nível de classe <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute> atributo, o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute> é ignorado, porque o valor de <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> é sempre `true`.

trans-unit.source: You can override the <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl" /> property to return <see langword="false" /> or to determine its value based on whether the wizard control is marked with a class-level <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute" />.
trans-unit.target: Você pode substituir o <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl" /> propriedade para retornar <see langword="false" /> ou para determinar seu valor com base em se o controle do assistente está marcado com um nível de classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute" />.

trans-unit.source: If the <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl" /> is not overridden, the designer ignores the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute" />.
trans-unit.target: Se o <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CreateUserWizardDesigner.UsePreviewControl" /> não é substituído, o designer ignora o <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute" />.
